awly.homepage.description.message: Your one-stop portal for following LoongArch upstream work

不出意外地，2023-2024 是龙架构基础生态建设风生水起的两年。在多数的基础.message: As expected, 2023-2024 were two thriving years of LoongArch. LoongArch support has been successfully mainlined in most infrastructure projects, and enjoys continued maintenance.

然而，外部形势波诡云谲，我们的事业面对着，并且仍将面对更多技术的、非技术的挑战乃.message: However, the external environment is ever more turbulent; our mission faces, and will continue to face, more challenges and risks both technical and non-technical: our workload and hardship are unprecedented in the face of broader use cases and more diverse user communities.

我们认为 2025-2026 是关键的转折点。世界瞬息万变，唯有终日乾乾、夕惕若.message: We believe 2025-2026 to be a critical period of transition. In the face of a world ever-changing, only by vigilance and perseverance can we see the light of day. Time to get down to work!
